Insider Activity


Individual




Richard Paul Schifter



Mr. Richard P. Schifter is Independent Director at American Airlines Group, Inc., Independent Director at EverBank Financial Corp., Lead Independent Director at LPL Financial Holdings, Inc., and a Member at The District of Columbia Bar. He is on the Board of Directors at American Airlines Group, Inc., EverBank, EverBank Financial Corp., LPL Financial Holdings, Inc., Bristol Group, Productora de Papeles SA, Empresas Chocolates la Corona SA, Diveo Broadband Networks, Inc., Controladora Milano SA de CV, Midwest Air Group, Inc., Tygris Commercial Finance Group, Inc., LPL Holdings, Inc., Youth, I.N.C. USA, Direct General Corp., and ProSight Specialty Insurance Holdings, Inc.
Mr. Schifter was previously employed as Lead Independent Director by Republic Airways Holdings, Inc. and Partner by Arnold & Porter LLP. He also served on the board at NYMAGIC, Inc., Midwest Airlines, Inc., US Airways Group, Inc., US Airways, Inc., Endurance Specialty Holdings Ltd., Ariel Reinsurance Co. Ltd., Ryanair Holdings Plc, America West Airlines, Inc., America West Holdings Corp., Grupo Milano SA de CV, American Airlines, Inc., and EcoEnterprises Fund.
He received his undergraduate degree from George Washington University and a graduate degree from The University of Pennsylvania Law School.



